Title: KitchenAid — At the Heart of Home
Author: wavelet-director

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - MORNING

A creamy KitchenAid Artisan stand mixer sits on a butcher-block counter, bathed in soft window light. A hand sets a brown egg down beside it. Stillness.

CUT TO:

INT. MIXING BOWL - MORNING

Macro: the spiral dough hook folds a pale buttery dough over itself, slow rotation, light glinting off burnished metal.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

The camera dollies slowly backward. The mixer holds the center of frame, its iconic silhouette unchanged. A woman's hand reaches in and lifts the tilt-head.

FADE OUT.
